cs.CV, cs.IT, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM

The paper discusses a deep learning approach for CT reconstruction, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV). The paper also introduces a mathematical theory for the U-net architecture, which involves signal processing and information theory (cs.IT). The use of deep learning and the development of new architectures also falls under machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Finally, the application of the proposed method to medical imaging also falls under multimedia (cs.MM).
